# Every value here is OPTIONAL — `npm run dev` works with no .env at all (keyless defaults).
# Uncomment/override any of these for a longer backfill or production.

# Historical backfill from SQD Portal. Defaults to the free public Portal (no key needed).
# PORTAL_URL_1=https://portal.sqd.dev/datasets/ethereum-mainnet
# PORTAL_API_KEY=                       # only for a dedicated/keyed portal

# Realtime tip + the vault-metadata readContract calls. Defaults to a keyless *archive* public
# RPC (eth.drpc.org) — the vault reads happen at historical blocks, so a non-archive node rejects
# them. Rate-limits under load; set your own for real work:
# PONDER_RPC_URL_1=https://eth.your-archive-rpc.example

# Backfill window. Defaults to a ~91k-block demo (start 20529207 → +91000). Widen for more:
# PONDER_START=20529207
# PONDER_END=25436954
# PONDER_FULL=1   # run the full history (no endBlock bound)
